SUMMARY:Valued Volunteers Training
DESCRIPTION:There are so many different ways you can get involved in SDoL\, and we encourage parents and community members to utilize their talents and knowledge by serving as volunteers throughout the District. \nSDoL welcomes you to share your time and expertise with our students. We know that we cannot do this work alone\, but TOGETHER WE CAN. We celebrate the amazing resources our volunteers bring to our schools and students every day!
URL:https://sdlancaster.org/event/valued-volunteers-training/
CATEGORIES:All Events
END:VEVENT
